parsed.explanation: Corrected the malformed opening tag for <TITLE> (removing the stray double quote). Also corrected five instances of corrupted character sequences (e.g., '\u221a\u00b7', '\u221a\u00a7', '\u221a\u00fc', '\u221a\u2202') which were intended to represent German umlauts (ü, ä, ö) and the sharp S (ß).
